text: Patrīcija Eiduka in 2018 Patrīcija Eiduka (born 1 February 2000) is a cross- country skier from Latvia.FIS profile She started skiing at three in Vecbebri. Patrīcija Eiduka competed for Latvia at the 2018 Winter Olympics.Pyeongchang 2018 profile == References == Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Cross-country skiers at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Latvian female cross-country skiers Category:Olympic cross-country skiers of Latvia
